reviewText: I forgot how much I loved Westerns as a kid.  These are those cheezy and wonderful Westerns I spent hours watching on TV.  Ah for the days when honor and ethics and a man's word was law.  Not just fun, but a trip back to a different America.  One I wish was still around.
